## How much does Northbeam cost in 2026?

Northbeam uses pageview-based pricing across three tiers. Unlike competitors who price by GMV (Triple Whale) or ad spend (Cometly), Northbeam scales with your website traffic volume.

### How do Northbeam's tiers compare?

| Feature | Starter MTA | Professional MTA | Enterprise MTA |
|---------|-------------|-----------------|----------------|
| **Price** | $999-1,500/mo | $2,500-3,500/mo | Custom |
| **Pageview limit** | Up to 1M/month | 1M+ monthly | High-volume |
| **Data refresh** | 4x daily | Hourly | Hourly+ |
| **Multi-touch attribution** | Yes | Yes | Yes |
| **Shopify integration** | Yes | Yes | Yes |
| **Ad platform integrations** | Yes | Yes | Yes |
| **Creative analytics** | No | Yes | Yes |
| **API access** | No | Yes | Yes |
| **MMM+ (budgeting/forecasting)** | No | Yes | Yes |
| **Multi-domain** | 1 domain | Up to 3 domains | Unlimited |
| **Media strategist reviews** | No | Included | 18/year |
| **Incrementality testing** | No | No | Coming soon |
| **Payment terms** | Month-to-month | Quarterly/annual | Custom |

