## Is Northbeam worth the price?

Northbeam is a serious DTC attribution tool with genuine technical depth. ML fractional attribution, creative analytics, and MMM+ are valuable for brands spending significantly on ads. The $999/mo Starter tier is reasonable for the capability, but the feature cliff to Professional ($2,500/mo) is steep.

If you're an enterprise DTC brand ($40M+) with dedicated media buyers, Northbeam Professional can prevent enough wasted ad spend to justify its cost. For smaller brands or those who want to inspect their attribution models rather than trust a black box, cheaper alternatives deliver core attribution at a fraction of the price.

